---
// src/components/content-conversion/AIConversionSupport.astro
---
<section class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-12 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="lg:w-1/2">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6 leading-tight">
          AI Helps Speed Up Conversion, But Humans Shape the Learning
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-brand-textMuted leading-relaxed mb-6">
          TheEduAssist can use AI-assisted workflows to summarize long content, extract key ideas, create first-draft lesson structures, identify quiz ideas, and repurpose material faster. Human review remains central so the final content is accurate, clear, learner-friendly, and platform-ready.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:w-1/2 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        {[
          "AI-assisted summarization",
          "Topic extraction",
          "Lesson draft support",
          "Quiz and worksheet ideas",
          "Human review",
          "Platform-ready formatting"
        ].map((item, index) => (
          <div class={`p-4 rounded-xl border flex items-center space-x-3 ${index >= 4 ? 'bg-brand-softGreen/30 border-brand-accent/30' : 'bg-brand-softBg border-brand-border/60'}`}>
             <svg class={`w-5 h-5 shrink-0 ${index >= 4 ? 'text-brand-accent' : 'text-brand-textMuted'}`} fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
             <span class="font-semibold text-brand-navy text-sm">{item}</span>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
